== small caps ==
Why these small caps? I cannot see any reason of the current usage. [[User:Mootros|Mootros]] ([[User talk:Mootros|talk]]) 08:36, 10 September 2012 (UTC) :Convention in military writing is to capitalise operation names. Smallcaps seemed the sensible way to acomplish this. --'''[[user:ErrantX|Errant]]''' <sup>([[User_talk:ErrantX|chat!]])</sup> 10:47, 10 September 2012 (UTC)
