== Contradictory statements ==
"The larger of the two operations, Taxable was carried out by 18 small boats… During this time only a small German response was observed including searchlights and intermittent gunfire… Taxable did not appear to have the desired effect and failed to elicit any response from the Germans."
Which was it, a small response or no response at all? [[User:Kaldari|Kaldari]] ([[User talk:Kaldari|talk]]) 04:16, 6 June 2014 (UTC) :Both :) I mean it to explain that there was a small local response but no actual troop movements in response to possible landings. On my phone right now but I can clarify it when I get online later :) --'''[[user:ErrantX|Errant]]''' <sup>([[User_talk:ErrantX|chat!]])</sup> 17:21, 6 June 2014 (UTC)
